        </head>
    </head>

    <body style="background-image: linear-gradient(#bad072, #d5e2ed);">
        
        <div align='center'>
            <h1>Categories Section</h1>
            <h4>This is how the basic layout of the questions will be:</h4>
        </div>
        
        
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row" id="results" margin="5px;" style="background-color:rgb(213, 226, 237)">
                <div class="col-sm"> <div>Attempts: </div> <h5 id="attemptsLeft">4</h5> </div>
                <div class="col-sm"> <div>Correct Questions: </div> <h5 id="correctAnswersShow">0</h5></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        
        <div class='container' id="categories_game" style="background-color:rgb(213, 226, 237)">
            <div class='jumbotron' style="background-color:rgb(213, 226, 237)">
                <div align='center'  style="background-color:rgb(213, 226, 237)">
                     
                    <strong>
                        <p>*Question Name*</p>    
                    </strong>
                    
                    <br>
                    
                    <strong>
                        <p>*Answer Choice A*</p>
                        <p>*Answer Choice B*</p>
                        <p>*Answer Choice C*</p>
                        <p>*Answer Choice D*</p>
                    </strong>
                    
                    <br>Enter either A, B, C, or D<br>
                    
                    <input id='answer' name='answer' placeholder'insert answer here' required>
                    
                    </br>
                    </br>
                    
                    </br>
                    <button class='btn btn-primary btn-lg'>Enter</button>
                    
                </div>
            
                </br>
                </br>
                
                
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div align='center'>
            <h4>You will have 30 seconds for each question.  The questions will be C++ related that scale in difficulty.  Make sense?</h4>
            <button class='btn btn-success' id='inputsButton' onClick='getStarted()'>Start</button>
        </div>

        <script src='jswork/categories.js'></script>
    </body>
</html>